text:
Yankees pitcher James Paxton wanted a protective “L screen” in front of the mound before his simulated innings, after Masahiro Tanaka took a line drive to the head. 

Tanaka is under MLB concussion protocol. "We’ll take it day by day," Aaron Boone said.

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Amid protests, costly delays and a legal issues, the 600-mile Atlantic Coast Pipeline project is cancelled.

The natural-gas pipeline would've tunneled under the Appalachian Trail from W. Va. to N.C.

Two energy companies worked on it for 6 years.
